        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You have learned how to create perpetual alchemical infusions that can provide a near-infinite supply of certain simple items.</p>\n<p>You gain the ability to create two 1st-level alchemical items using @Compendium[pf2e.classfeatures.Quick Alchemy]{Quick Alchemy} without spending a batch of infused reagents. The items you can select depend on your research field and must be in your formula book.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Choose two of the following formulas:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf2e.equipment-srd.Bestial Mutagen (Lesser)]{Bestial Mutagen (Lesser)},</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf2e.equipment-srd.Cognitive Mutagen (Lesser)]{Cognitive Mutagen (Lesser)},</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf2e.equipment-srd.Juggernaut Mutagen (Lesser)]{Juggernaut Mutagen (Lesser)},</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf2e.equipment-srd.Quicksilver Mutagen (Lesser)]{Quicksilver Mutagen (Lesser)},</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf2e.equipment-srd.Serene Mutagen (Lesser)]{Serene Mutagen (Lesser)}, or</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf2e.equipment-srd.Silvertongue Mutagen (Lesser)]{Silvertongue Mutagen (Lesser)}</li>\n</ul>"
